Name: Average resolution time for 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' cases.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Difference in average resolution time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Difference in average resolution time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Request Payment'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time elapsed for all instances of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' across all cases.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the next activity in the process.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' for cases that were eventually approved.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Payment Handled' across all cases.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Difference in minimum resolution time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time it takes for a case to be resolved after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING', compared to the average time it takes for a case to be resolved after 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for all instances of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to reach 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases where the declaration is resubmitted.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to the final activity in the process for cases that are eventually rejected at a later stage.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case
